items.name: ABORT
desc: An operation was aborted.

items.name: ACCESS_DENIED
desc: An object cannot be accessed due to insufficient user rights.

items.name: ALREADY_EXISTING
desc: An object already exists.

items.name: BAD_CRC
desc: A bad checksum.

items.name: CANT_CREATE
desc: An object could not be created.

items.name: CANT_READ
desc: Data could not be read from a file.

items.name: CANT_SEEK
desc: A seek operation could not be run.

items.name: CANT_TELL
desc: A tell operation could not be run.

items.name: CANT_WRITE
desc: Data could not be written to a file.

items.name: CURRENT_DIRECTORY
desc: A function is not possible because the path contains the current directory.

items.name: DEVICE_NOT_READY
desc: A device (drive) not ready.

items.name: DIFFERENT_DEVICES
desc: A function is not possible because the devices (drives) are not identical.

items.name: GENERAL
desc: A general input/output error.

items.name: INVALID_ACCESS
desc: An invalid attempt was made to access an object.

items.name: INVALID_CHARACTER
desc: A file name contains invalid characters.

items.name: INVALID_DEVICE
desc: A specified device is invalid.

items.name: INVALID_LENGTH
desc: Invalid data length.

items.name: INVALID_PARAMETER
desc: An operation was started with an invalid parameter.

items.name: IS_WILDCARD
desc: An operation cannot be run on file names containing wildcards.

items.name: LOCKING_VIOLATION
desc: A locking problem.

items.name: MISPLACED_CHARACTER
desc: An invalid file name.

items.name: NAME_TOO_LONG
desc: A file name is too long.

items.name: NOT_EXISTING
desc: A nonexistent object.

items.name: NOT_EXISTING_PATH
desc: The path to a file does not exist.

items.name: NOT_SUPPORTED
desc: An action is not supported.

items.name: NO_DIRECTORY
desc: An object is not a directory.

items.name: NO_FILE
desc: An object is not a file.

items.name: OUT_OF_DISK_SPACE
desc: No more space on a device.

items.name: OUT_OF_FILE_HANDLES
desc: No more file handles available.

items.name: OUT_OF_MEMORY
desc: An operation could not be run due to insufficient memory.

items.name: PENDING
desc: An operation is still pending.

items.name: RECURSIVE
desc: An object cannot be copied into itself.

items.name: UNKNOWN
desc: Unknown.
An unknown I/O error has occurred.

items.name: WRITE_PROTECTED
desc: A function is not possible because the object is write protected.

items.name: WRONG_FORMAT
desc: An incorrect file format.

items.name: WRONG_VERSION
desc: An incorrect file version.
